title: Season Rewards
body: Hello guys,i dont want to be annoying,and i read about it and saw when you said that all players will get ther rewards,but it is 6 days when all get it and i  just want to ask when i will get it ? ty for your time :)

replies.body: Some players on EU region haven't received their rewards yet, per the [service status](http://status.leagueoflegends.com/#eune).  I'd suggest submitting a [support ticket](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/requests/new) to look into your specific issue individually.  We'll respond back asap!
